item.title: CVE-2020-5356|2024-09-16T19:36:53.503Z -- dell -- power%20protect%20data%20manager
item.description: Dell PowerProtect Data Manager (PPDM) versions prior to 19.4 and Dell PowerProtect X400 versions prior to 3.2 contain an improper authorization vulnerability. A remote authenticated malicious user may download any file from the affected PowerProtect virtual machines.
